  "body": "Weird stuff happens when using this markdown symbol ` for text formatting. When using a space after the 2nd symbol to close the formatting, the 2nd symbol gets removed. In case of a line break including text that followed the symbol https://www.loom.com/share/12086d855c85459686cac5eb4bf22492\r\n\r\n### Current\r\n` seems supported, but when used the issue occurs that text is removed\r\n\r\n### Expected\r\n` is not supported or can be used without text being removed when using space or when the symbol is used after a line break",
